item.description: This webinar is about a project I led while working at MRCagney. I led the development of an online housing capacity model for Whang훮rei. The model computes the plan-enabled and commercially feasible housing capacity of the urban environment of Whang훮rei. It was developed to help the Council meet the statutory requirements of the National Policy Statement on Urban Development (2020).
